        "gpt-4o-mini"
      ]
    },
    "long_instructions": "##Processor Comparison Assistant\r\n\r\nThis chatbot helps you figure out which kind of processor (CPU, GPU, ASIC, or FPGA) is best for a specific task related to an AI model that you are examining. Here's how to get started:\r\n\r\n1. Think of a task you want to know more about. \r\n\r\n> **Example**: _“Which processor is best for voice recognition?”_ or _“What should I use for training an AI model?”_\r\n\r\n2. Type your question into the chat. The chatbot will give you a short, clear explanation of which processor is best for that task and why.\r\n3. Want to learn more? The chatbot will offer a follow-up question if you’re curious and want to dig deeper!\r\n\r\n",
